<br>
I get this a lot from caster types...(especially pet classes)<br>
<br>
they insist on being allowed to start a fight fully buffed (and pet buffed) and full mana.....bull.<br>
<br>
If they want a good fight...then agree....start fight with ZERO buffs. give 30 seconds for buffage/medding...then engage. That is a fair fight.<br>
<br>
Warrior have no buffage ability apart from a few right clickies...so level the field. I have a friend who refused to duel unless he gets like 10 mins to buff and med....which is silly. Be ready to fight fast and furious.<br>
<br>
Also, I would recommend you get your hands on the likes of a silken whip of ensnaring or the likes, jboots, dot weapons are sweet, a right clickie like grim aura earing. shamy DS potion is good, a good high delay 2hs for jousting, good damage arrows if you are rooted (and good for jousting too),DISARM DISARM DISARM. Also get your buttons set up nicely so you can swap weapons about easily.<br>
<br>
